{"tid":1823524,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"假如達哥賣咗間日出康城，搞隻新嘅手機game，兄弟們會原諒他嗎？","createTime":"2020-01-13T18:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T00:37:34.000Z","uid":73381,"like":41,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"b9978584ea2057997d378bb46cf2053802532fda","tid":1823524,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:21:16.000Z","msg":"達哥:<br />\n<br />\n- 有人話我剝削員工. 無錯, 我搞依隻game要剝削好多人, 尤其係剝削自己.<br />\n<br />\n- 我自己完全無收酬勞, 而且自己仲要賣咗自己層樓去籌錢搞game.<br />\n<br />\n- 我賣樓出手機game, 就係因為唔想隻game變成大陸game, 唔想接受「中共審查」.<br />\n<br />\n- 隻遊戲目標觀眾係香港人.<br />\n<br />\n-  以我隻game的 budget, 我係無咩可能返本, 但我可以唔駛接受「中共審查」, 自由自在地開發.<br />\n<br />\n- 有人鬧我隻game係深圳研發, 好抱歉.  我整呢隻game需要50天, 但以我的 budget, 如果完全係香港研發, 只得15天搞.<br />\n<br />\n- 有人可以用15天就可以完成一隻game, 但我真係唔得, 對唔住.<br />\n<br />\n- 全行都認為我係傻佬, 賣咗層樓整手遊, 90 % 無得翻盤, 我希望講返真實情況畀大家聽, 玩唔玩, 唔係好緊要"},{"pid":"6163de6467c1a977112f8fea8d5c171badf8230a","tid":1823524,"uid":63311,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:21:49.000Z","msg":"達狗點會咁做"},{"pid":"e283efd219a77aee3355133c1ecaee8e3a72e9e5","tid":1823524,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"6163de6467c1a977112f8fea8d5c171badf8230a","tid":1823524,"uid":63311,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:21:49.000Z","msg":"達狗點會咁做"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:23:43.000Z","msg":"假如佢真係做 你會支持嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6ea02e4fd171cac12b3f062cbefa3e9c0a0a88","tid":1823524,"uid":42283,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e283efd219a77aee3355133c1ecaee8e3a72e9e5","tid":1823524,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"6163de6467c1a977112f8fea8d5c171badf8230a","tid":1823524,"uid":63311,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:21:49.000Z","msg":"達狗點會咁做"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:23:43.000Z","msg":"假如佢真係做 你會支持嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class